{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437700/extras/ShowcaseGIF.gif?t=1738380259\" /><u>BACKGROUND</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a post-apocalyptic world devoid of human life, the last vestiges of humanity's existence lie in the actions of abandoned service robots. These automata, designed to follow commands without question, continue to carry out their final orders long after their masters perished. Some maintain crumbling estates, tending to overgrown gardens and polishing furniture in empty mansions. Others patrol desolate streets, enforcing long-forgotten rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Their unwavering loyalty creates a haunting world in which remnants of human civilization persist in strange, surreal ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over time, some robots have developed quirks in their programming, leading to unexpected behaviours.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>GAMEPLAY</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cast your line, wait patiently, and start reeling in once you\u2019ve hooked a fish.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437700/extras/ReelingGIF.gif?t=1738380259\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover and unlock new fishing areas to expand your adventure.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3437700/extras/ExplorationGIF.gif?t=1738380259\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather materials through purchases or exploration, then craft and upgrade your fishing tackle for better performance.</p><p class=\"bb_pa